<p>It is worth stressing that in this representation the matrix 
 <bold>X</bold> is known, while the matrices 
 <bold>W</bold> and 
 <bold>H</bold> are unknown and determined by the NMF algorithm. In particular, we used a variation of the NMF algorithm that minimizes the Kullback-Leibler divergence loss function [
 <xref rid="pcbi.1006173.ref052" ref-type="bibr">52</xref>] defined as follows: 
